                            <comment id="276770" author="adilger" created="Wed, 5 Aug 2020 21:47:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This version exception should really be moved into &lt;tt&gt;test_2c&lt;/tt&gt; as a &lt;tt&gt;skip&lt;/tt&gt; (along with all of the other version checks at the start of &lt;tt&gt;sanity-lfsck&lt;/tt&gt;), rather than keeping them in &lt;tt&gt;ALWAYS_EXCEPT&lt;/tt&gt; since that is for defects in the code/test that are temporarily being skipped, not because of permanent gaps in functionality.  Will leave the &lt;tt&gt;always_except&lt;/tt&gt; label until that is done.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="74771" author="yujian" created="Sat, 11 Jan 2014 13:42:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for Lustre 2.5.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="74363" author="bobijam" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 15:35:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch for b2_5 tracking at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8728&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8728&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
