&lt;p&gt;The same failure occurred:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cb204dda-74f6-11e3-95ae-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cb204dda-74f6-11e3-95ae-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hi Oleg,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please cherry-pick patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8386&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8386&lt;/a&gt; to Lustre b2_5 branch? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72373" author="yong.fan" created="Wed, 27 Nov 2013 07:47:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch has been landed to master.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72211" author="yong.fan" created="Mon, 25 Nov 2013 06:12:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is the patch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/8386/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/8386/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72210" author="yong.fan" created="Mon, 25 Nov 2013 06:04:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lustre-2.4 does not support test_2c, will skip it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="72192" author="adilger" created="Sat, 23 Nov 2013 17:43:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are a number of tests failing in master-2.4 interop tests when running the &quot;full&quot; test suite. This test should just be skipped in interop mode if it doesn&apos;t make sense to run. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
